script = ExtResource("3_45cx5")
category = 23
text = "believe fuyan is the pursuit of mastery
get their metal from the Zengef and Manok

Roroni has one big clan in the middle of their territory which has Warrior Societies that specialise in specific weapons
		Dancing Swords - Rapiers and a dancing avoiding style
		Blackblades - Black Greatswords (made of a special material?) and aspis shields
		Spearbonded - Use spears, sickles and short spears aka javelins they throw, treat their spear as sacred
		Strongfists - Fight with like hooped blades on their fists
		Jabpoles - Polearms, Glaives

People's Societies
		Molten Hammers - Blacksmiths, very renowned

wind spear guy in roroni
	part of the spearbonded
	uses a sickle sword to catch swords
	has quick reflex, can transform projectiles into wind then disperse it
	catches enemies sword throws it away and transform it into wind
	carries javelin he throws, enhances with wind
	wears a hoop thingy to hold his sickles (has 2 and sometimes uses both) but primarily uses his spear"
id = 42
name = "Roroni Ideas"
